reviewText: excellent view of Andre's personal life and him backstage. a lot in English, so you don't have to read a lot of transcripts, Only at the beginning of this dvd do you

The second in this series. It continues to give a delightful view of how the orchestra interacts and  behaves off-stage, and what it takes to put on Andre's incredible performances. More wonderful music.
Andre  is  the best  musician and  conductor  in our day  We  have all  of his available  music  since  we first knew of him  We did attend one of his concerts and he never disappoints
I love andre Rieu, yes it is wonderful to see how Andre works behind the scenes.  He is magic!

I'M SO GLAD ANDRE DECIDED TO PROVIDE HIS FOLLOWING WITH A LITTLE MORE ABOUT HIS BEHIND-THE-SCENE INFO.
WELL WORTH YOUR VIEWING TIME.
